title: 09/20 Fantasy Football Podcast: Buy Low, Sell High; LAR-SF
description:
Need to improve your team? We've got plenty of buy low and sell high candidates on today's show including our favorite buy low guys (4:08) at the top of the show. Are we concerned about any elite WRs? ... More buy low candidates (20:50): How legit is Carson Wentz (22:22)? Buy Cam Newton (29:44)? Isaiah Crowell (31:24)? Sell high on Derrick Henry (32:20)? Mike Gillislee (40:30)? ... Previewing LAR-SF (43:45), anyone to start other than the RBs? Then it's on to your questions, Team Name Tuesday on a Wednesday (49:50) and Grade the Trade at the end of the show ... Your emails at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
